==Russian==

===Conditional particle===
'''[[бы]]''', '''б''' (by, b)

# [[бы]] (often shortened to [[б#Russian|б]]) is a verbal particle used to render [[conditional]] and [[subjunctive]] patterns:
#:: [[я#Russian|Я]] [[говорить|говорил]] — ''I spoke''
#: [[я#Russian|Я]] бы [[говорить|говорил]] — ''I would (should) have spoken; I would speak; I might speak'' 
#: [[я#Russian|Я]] [[говорить|говорил]] [[бы]] — ''I would (should) have spoken; I would speak; I might speak'' 

'''N.B.''' — [[бы]] is the [[third-person singular]] [[aorist]] of [[быть]] ''(to be)'', an otherwise obsolete Russian tense.

